<h1>Fax configuration and troubleshooting.</h1>
<p class="lede">VoiceTel supports electronic fax delivery in both directions — inbound DIDs routed to email and outbound faxes sent by email through the VoiceTel fax domain. Articles in this section cover routing, destination email setup, outbound formatting, and authorization.</p>
